partnerDetails.about:
Operating since 1975, We at Central Electricals and Electronics Pvt Ltd believe in providing quick response and ace solutions for submetering needs for all clients.

We have developed a deep understanding of energy and utility metering requirements. We have built a reputation as a trusted partner and provider for the supply of sub-metering solutions to the network managers, panel builders and OEMs.
